OL,3,CReform UK ban on local press 'won't
OL,4,Cend until newspaper apologises'
OL,6,FIn his first interview since the ban,
OL,7,Fcouncil leader Mick Barton told ITV
OL,8,FNews Central he will not speak to
OL,9,FNottingham Post reporters again until
OL,10,Fhe receives "a full apology".
OL,12,F"The one thing I am every day in my
OL,13,Fworking life is professional, but
OL,14,Funfortunately I think from their point
OL,15,Fof view they haven't been totally
OL,16,Fprofessional.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
