OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F371A1756819586
OL,3,CReform UK ban on local press 'won't
OL,4,Cend until newspaper apologises'
OL,6,F"They asked me for opinions but they
OL,7,Fweren't putting out what I said. They
OL,8,Fwere spinning what I said, cutting it
OL,9,Fin half, making it say something
OL,10,Fdifferent.
OL,12,F"I need a full apology and then a way
OL,13,Fof working forward that's
OL,14,Fprofessional," he said.
OL,16,FThe ban means the paper, which has
OL,17,Fbeen delivering news to the city since
OL,18,F1878, cannot talk to councillors in
OL,19,Fany capacity, except in emergency
OL,20,Fscenarios like flooding.
