OL,3,CReform UK ban on local press 'won't
OL,4,Cend until newspaper apologises'
OL,6,FIt also applies to Local Democracy
OL,7,Freporters, of which ITV News Central
OL,8,Fand other news outlets often use.
OL,10,FThe ban, which has been criticised by
OL,11,Funion bosses as a blow to democracy,
OL,12,Fcame into force after an article was
OL,13,Fpublished claiming that two Reform
OL,14,Fcounty councillors would be suspended
OL,15,Ffrom their county council group if
OL,16,Fthey did not vote for Cllr Barton's
OL,17,Fpreference of a bigger Nottingham
OL,18,Fcovering Broxtowe and Gedling.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
