OL,3,CReform UK ban on local press 'won't
OL,4,Cend until newspaper apologises'
OL,6,FCllr Barton said this story was "total
OL,7,Ffolly" and "really upset one of the
OL,8,Fcouncillors".
OL,10,FWhen asked if he had investigated
OL,11,Fwhether these claims were true, Cllr
OL,12,FBarton said he "didn't have to"
OL,13,Fbecause his councillors had told them
OL,14,Fit wasn't true.
OL,16,FHe added: "I take my councillors
OL,17,Fopinions very seriously and I've stood
OL,18,Fby them."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
