OL,3,CReform UK ban on local press 'won't
OL,4,Cend until newspaper apologises'
OL,6,FHe also said he was not banning
OL,7,Fcouncillors from talking to anyone, if
OL,8,Fthey wanted to, but he was simply not
OL,9,Fallowing press releases to be sent to
OL,10,Fthe news outlet.
OL,12,FNatalie Fahy, the editor of
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Live and Nottingham
OL,14,FPost, told ITV News Central: "Seven
OL,15,Fdays into the ban, I'm still
OL,16,Fabsolutely shocked that a politician
OL,17,Fwould do this to the free press.
OL,19,F"This is an attack on our democracy.
OL,20,FIt's straight out of the Reform
OL,21,Fplaybook.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
