OL,3,CReform UK ban on local press 'won't
OL,4,Cend until newspaper apologises'
OL,6,F"We're not here to be biased, we're
OL,7,Fjust asking questions. The article
OL,8,Fthat got us banned is not only
OL,9,Faccurate... but it's an important
OL,10,Fissue we're trying to bring to light
OL,11,Fto people because it's going to cost
OL,12,Fthe taxpayer a lot of money."
OL,14,FCllr Barton told ITV News he had "no
OL,15,Fissue with speaking to any
OL,16,Fjournalist", but had banned
OL,17,FNottinghamshire Live because they had
OL,18,F"made it personal" towards him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
