OL,3,CReform UK ban on local press 'won't
OL,4,Cend until newspaper apologises'
OL,6,FIn response, Ms Fahy said: "It's
OL,7,Fcertainly not a personal attack on
OL,8,FMick Barton. Why would it be? We're
OL,9,Fjust doing our jobs.
OL,11,F"I'm happy to resolve the issue
OL,12,Famicably. I've dealt with so many
OL,13,Fcouncil leaders over rough patches in
OL,14,Fmy 20 years as a journalist. But we
OL,15,Fwon't be apologising, we've got
OL,16,Fnothing to apologise for."
